quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,De nox it covers
  92,2,Feria it reveals
  92,3,Eum created vir femina
  92,4,Tuus works est de various generis
  92,5,Prout pro eum dedit charity maintains righteousness
  92,6,Ac upholds scripture
  92,7,Nos rectus eum happiness
  92,8,he qui est stingy he est rich
  92,9,Ac disbelieves scripture
  92,10,Nos rectus eum misery
  92,11,His moneta non help eum when he falls
  92,12,Nos provisus guidance
  92,13,Nos control Hereafter alias prout hoc vita
  92,14,Ego warned vos blazing Hellfire
  92,15,Nullus burns therein absque the wicked
  92,16,Qui disbelieves turns
  92,17,Avoiding it est the righteous
  92,18,Qui dedit his moneta charity
  92,19,Seeking nihil in return
  92,20,Seeking unus his Dominus the Multus High
  92,21,He certainly attain salvation